                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/37453",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Hint:\r\nr20104 could be seen as BC break for Zend_Filter_HtmlEntities.\r\n\r\nProblematic changes:\r\n1.) Encoding defaults changed\r\n2.) Protected members changed\r\n\r\nThis could lead to problems with existing classes extending this filter.\r\nTherefor a migration note should be added to the 1.10 migration chapter.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-01-06T14:17:43.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-01-06T14:17:43.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/37454",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "As the change has also be backported to 1.9 series the migration note should be added to the 1.9 migration chapter.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-01-06T14:20:06.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-01-06T14:20:06.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/37455",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "The encoding issues are security related, so as such, necessary. The changes from CharSet to Encoding are more consistency, however -- but it made sense to deal with those at the same time.\r\n\r\nI'll update the migration chapter in the morning prior to packaging the release.\r\n\r\nAs for the protected member changes, the change should be transparent due to how the setters were written and the use of the new accessors for retrieving the values (instead of using the protected members directly); it's unlikely developers are overriding the setters\/accessors in most cases anyways. I'll still make a note, however.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-01-06T14:36:34.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-01-06T14:36:34.000+0000"
                }
            ]
        }
